    <item>
      <title>特朗普称其总统任期内不会建造风力发电场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-says-he-wants-no-wind-turbines-built-during-administration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普周二表示，他将在第二任期内推行不建造风电场的政策，这将对价值数十亿美元的风电项目计划造成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-says-he-wants-no-wind-turbines-built-during-administration</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:37:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称北约国家应将 GDP 的 5% 用于国防</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-says-nato-nations-should-spend-5-of-gdp-on-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[候任总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，北约国家应该将相当于其经济产出的 5% 用于国防，他对欧洲盟友的要求是目前目标的两倍以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-says-nato-nations-should-spend-5-of-gdp-on-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:37:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 首席执行官表示很高兴与特朗普会面并向他表示祝贺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/nvidia-ceo-says-he-d-be-delighted-to-meet-and-congratulate-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人工智能热潮中心人物、英伟达公司首席执行官黄仁勋表示，他已准备好与美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普会面，并为新一届政府提供帮助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/nvidia-ceo-says-he-d-be-delighted-to-meet-and-congratulate-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普升级对加拿大、格陵兰和巴拿马的威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-won-t-rule-out-us-military-taking-greenland-panama-canal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普在周二的新闻发布会上详细介绍了寻求扩大美国对格陵兰岛、加拿大和巴拿马运河影响力的计划，并拒绝排除使用军事或经济胁迫手段的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-won-t-rule-out-us-military-taking-greenland-panama-canal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:08:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佛罗里达州美国法官阻止特别检察官提交特朗普报告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/florida-judge-blocks-release-of-special-counsel-s-trump-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州一名联邦法官阻止司法部发布针对唐纳德·特朗普的两项刑事调查报告，这可能导致这位当选总统与调查他的检察官之间发生法律纠纷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/florida-judge-blocks-release-of-special-counsel-s-trump-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:01:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
